Holly-Humberstone-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Holly-Humberstone-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/holly-humberstone">Holly Humberstone</a>分享了在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lollapalooza">Lollapalooza 2023</a>上与<a href="/artists/d4vd">D4vid</a>合作制作歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/holly-humberstone-and-d4vd-team-up-on-new-track-superbloodmoon-3475006">“Superbloodmoon”</a>的感受。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tomorrow-x-together-lollapalooza-2023-live-review-3478932">Tomorrow X Together 在 2023 年 Lollapalooza 现场直播：回归的男孩乐队让成为节日头条新闻看起来很容易</a></strong></li></ul><p>在今年的芝加哥音乐节后台，Humberstone 接受<em>NME</em>采访时分享道：“与 D4vid 合作真是太酷了。自从他开始发行音乐以来，我一直是他的粉丝。他在英国巡演，我问他是否愿意进入工作室，我们就写了《超级血月》”</p><p>她继续说：“这首歌是关于远离家乡和与人脱节的感觉，我真的很喜欢它。我没有进行过很多合作，但这是一次非常愉快的经历。 [D4vid]是一个可爱的人，他的声音是如此流畅和华丽。我真的为这首歌感到自豪。”</p><p>在选择 D4vid 作为她在这首歌中的合作者时，这位歌手解释说他看起来是完美的选择。 </p><figure id="attachment_3475008" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3475008" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3475008" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hollyhumberstone_press_d4vd.jpg" alt="霍莉·亨伯斯通" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hollyhumberstone_press_d4vd.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hollyhumberstone_press_d4vd-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Hollyhumberstone_press_d4vd-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont